If statement [] <- reference to the test command
if [ condition ] 
then
	{COMMAND}
fi
Same as above:
if test condition
then
	{COMMAND}
fi

Else statement
if [ condition ]
then
	{Command 1}
else
	{Command 2}
fi

Elif statement:
if [ condition ]
then
	{Command 1}
elif [ condition ]
then
	{Command 2}
else 
	{Command 3}
fi
